--- Same Game Gravity For Desktop ---

Copyright (C) 2011 @greweb
Licence: GPL v3 - https://github.com/gre/same-game-gravity

Same Game Gravity is a mind-bending ball removal puzzle game where you try 
to remove all of the balls from the board. Balls can only be removed when 
they are grouped with more balls of the same color. 
The balls are influenced by gravity. 
